  <figcaption><p></p></figcaption>
</figure>

<p>$\solution$ <br />
Use the Vertical Line Test,</p>

<figure style="text-align: center;">
  <img src="/images/content/DC/DC-1.7.3.png" alt="my alt text" width="250px" />
  <figcaption><p></p></figcaption>
</figure>

<p>Since the vertical line intersects the graph more than once, it is <strong>NOT A FUNCTION</strong>.</p>

